                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7147" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0179</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10422 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG如何解燃“煤”之急？——双碳背景下“华润电力”转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How can ESG solve the urgent need for &quot;coal&quot;? ——The transformation of &quot;China Resources Power&quot; under the background of Carbon Peaking and Carbon Neutrality</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张倩，朱新超，魏媛媛，王宇鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑龙江科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华润电力控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源转型；ESG报告；企业社会责任；双碳；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Energy Transition; ESG Reporting; Corporate Social Responsibility; Carbon Neutrality; Sustainability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国生态文明建设的不断推进和“双碳目标”的提出，电力行业的低碳化发展已成必然，火电企业纷纷开展能源转型，布局清洁能源成为可持续发展的必由之路。华润电力作为国内火力发电的龙头企业之一，高污染高耗能的火电业务转型成为企业未来发展的燃“煤”之急，企业发展可再生能源是占领未来国内市场的关键一步。我国社会责任运动也随之不断发展，越来越多企业开始披露ESG报告，ESG成为推动企业高质量可持续发展的重要抓手。案例通过追溯华润电力近几年的发展历程，分析公司披露的ESG报告，剖析将ESG理念融入企业可持续发展战略的动因，依托ESG报告挖掘华润电力能源转型的举措。通过对华润电力案例的解读，帮助学员理解ESG的内涵，引导学员树立可持续发展观，探索传统火电企业的转型路径，提升企业综合价值，推动企业绿色高质量发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous advancement of China&#39;s ecological civilization construction and the proposal of the &quot; carbon peaking and carbon neutrality&quot;, the low-carbon development of the power industry has become inevitable, thermal power enterprises have carried out energy transformation, and the layout of clean energy has become the only way to sustainable development. As one of the leading enterprises of thermal power generation in China, the transformation of thermal power business with high pollution and high energy consumption has become the urgent need for the future development of enterprises, and the development of renewable energy is a key step in the layout of the future domestic market. China&#39;s social responsibility movement has also continued to develop, and more and more enterprises have begun to disclose ESG reports, and ESG has become an important starting point for promoting the high-quality and sustainable development of enterprises. By tracing the development process of CR Power in recent years, analyzing and summarizing the disclosed ESG report, analyzing the motivation for integrating ESG concepts into the company&#39;s sustainable development strategy, and relying on the ESG report to explore the measures of CR Power&#39;s energy transformation. Through the interpretation of the case of CR Power, it helps students understand the connotation of ESG, guides students to establish a sustainable development concept, explores the transformation path of traditional thermal power enterprises, enhances the comprehensive value of enterprises, and promotes the green and high-quality development of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分析企业内、外部压力，根据利益相关者理论分析缓解压力的方式；ESG理论、三重底线理论分析能源转型动因；战略性社会责任融合过程；华润电力实施绿色低碳电力的具体措施；华润电力实施ESG管理给企业带来的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
